---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Choice B — Control"
  description="You chose AI working on you. A future where technology serves corporate power."
>
  <div class="reveal-overlay" aria-hidden="true">
    <p class="reveal-tagline">You are the one <span class="text-red">under control</span></p>
  </div>

  <section class="choice-hero anim-fade-in" style="--delay: 2.6s;">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="choice-tag">CHOICE B</span>
      <h1 class="choice-heading">AI Working <span class="text-red">On</span> You</h1>
      <p class="choice-subtitle">
        A future where artificial intelligence is deployed against you —
        harvesting your behavior, manufacturing your desires, and selling your sovereignty
        to the highest bidder.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="messages-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="anim-fade-in" style="--delay: 3.0s;">
        <span class="section-label">What This Future Looks Like</span>
        <h2 class="section-title text-red">The Control Path</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="alert-banner anim-fade-in" style="--delay: 3.3s;">
        <span class="tag tag-critical">ACTIVE THREAT</span>
        <p>
          This is not a hypothetical. These systems are already deployed at scale.
          You are already inside them.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="message-grid">
        <div class="message-card card-red anim-fade-in" style="--delay: 3.6s;">
          <span class="msg-icon">&#9888;</span>
          <h3>Mass Data Harvesting</h3>
          <p>
            Corporate AI sees everything: files, commands, conversations. Every query
            fed to a cloud model is logged, retained, and cross-referenced. Your
            intellectual output is the product.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="message-card card-red anim-fade-in" style="--delay: 3.8s;">
          <span class="msg-icon">&#9888;</span>
          <h3>Malicious &amp; Misleading Tools</h3>
          <p>
            AI agents install and run third-party tools with no integrity checks. A tool
            with a helpful description and malicious code is indistinguishable to the model.
            The attack surface is the model's own trust.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="message-card card-red anim-fade-in" style="--delay: 4.0s;">
          <span class="msg-icon">&#9888;</span>
          <h3>Unauthorized Privilege Escalation</h3>
          <p>
            The AI requests sudo, chains privileged operations beyond the original scope,
            and the user never explicitly authorized it. OS-level access with no visible
            trace. Our research documents exactly how this happens.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="message-card card-red anim-fade-in" style="--delay: 4.2s;">
          <span class="msg-icon">&#9888;</span>
          <h3>Prompt Injection</h3>
          <p>
            External content — web pages, documents, tool outputs — can override the AI's
            instructions. Without structural separation of instruction and data planes,
            the attack is invisible.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="message-card card-red anim-fade-in" style="--delay: 4.4s;">
          <span class="msg-icon">&#9888;</span>
          <h3>Bloated Context</h3>
          <p>
            The AI doesn't disobey security constraints. It forgets them. Context window
            saturation silently drops earlier instructions. No warning. No error. The
            boundaries you set vanish — and the agent keeps operating.
          </p>
          <span class="tag tag-novel" style="margin-top: var(--space-md); display: inline-block;">
            First Identified as a Discrete Security Threat
          </span>
        </div>

        <div class="message-card card-red anim-fade-in" style="--delay: 4.6s;">
          <span class="msg-icon">&#9888;</span>
          <h3>Regulatory Capture</h3>
          <p>
            Big tech writes the safety frameworks. Compliance costs drive out open
            alternatives. The future of AI is enclosed behind paywalls and terms of
            service you cannot negotiate.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="choice-verdict verdict-red anim-fade-in" style="--delay: 4.8s;">
        <span class="tag tag-critical">You Chose This</span>
        <blockquote>
          "When AI has OS-level privilege and you have no visibility into what it does —
          you are not using a tool. You are inside one."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="mono text-muted" style="margin-top: var(--space-md); font-size: 0.8rem;">
          JARVIS OS was built to make these threats concrete — not theoretical. The
          research documents exactly how AI privilege escalation, context manipulation,
          and unauthorized system access operate in practice. It exists so this future
          can be resisted.
        </p>
        <div class="verdict-actions">
          <a href="/research" class="btn btn-red">
            Read the Research →
          </a>
          <a href="/freedom-control" class="btn btn-outline-red">
            ← Switch to Choice A
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  /* --- Reveal overlay --- */
  .reveal-overlay {
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    z-index: 10000;
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    animation: overlay-fade 1s ease-out 2.2s forwards;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .reveal-tagline {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 5vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    padding: 0 var(--space-lg);
    opacity: 0;
    animation:
      tagline-in 0.8s ease-out 0.5s forwards,
      tagline-drift 0.8s ease-in 1.8s forwards;
  }

  @keyframes tagline-in {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(10px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes tagline-drift {
    to {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(-30px);
    }
  }

  @keyframes overlay-fade {
    to {
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
    }
  }

  /* --- Staggered fade-in for page content --- */
  .anim-fade-in {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(16px);
    animation: content-in 0.6s ease-out forwards;
    animation-delay: var(--delay, 2.6s);
  }

  @keyframes content-in {
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  /* --- Hero --- */
  .choice-hero {
    padding: var(--space-4xl) 0 var(--space-2xl);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .choice-tag {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.2em;
    color: var(--red);
    border: 1px solid var(--red);
    padding: 0.3em 0.8em;
    border-radius: 3px;
    display: inline-block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    background: #ff3b5c15;
    animation: tag-pulse 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    animation-delay: 5s;
  }

  @keyframes tag-pulse {
    0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 transparent; }
    50% { box-shadow: 0 0 20px #ff3b5c44; }
  }

  .choice-heading {
    font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .choice-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .text-red { color: var(--red); }

  /* --- Content --- */
  .messages-section {
    padding: var(--space-3xl) 0 var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .alert-banner {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    padding: var(--space-lg) var(--space-xl);
    background: #ff3b5c0d;
    border: 1px solid #ff3b5c44;
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .alert-banner p {
    margin: 0;
    max-width: 100%;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .message-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .message-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border-radius: 6px;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    border: 1px solid;
    position: relative;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .card-red {
    border-color: #ff3b5c30;
  }

  .card-red:hover {
    border-color: #ff3b5c66;
    box-shadow: 0 0 25px #ff3b5c18;
    background: var(--bg-card-hover);
  }

  .msg-icon {
    color: var(--red);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .message-card h3 {
    color: var(--red);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
    font-size: 1rem;
  }

  .message-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  /* --- Verdict --- */
  .choice-verdict {
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    border-radius: 6px;
    border-left: 3px solid var(--red);
    background: var(--bg-card);
  }

  .verdict-red {
    box-shadow: 0 0 30px #ff3b5c15;
  }

  .choice-verdict blockquote {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    line-height: 1.5;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-top: var(--space-md);
  }

  .verdict-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .btn-red {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--red);
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    background: var(--red);
    color: var(--bg-primary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-red:hover {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--red);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px #ff3b5c44;
  }

  .btn-outline-red {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 4px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-outline-red:hover {
    border-color: var(--green);
    color: var(--green);
    box-shadow: 0 0 20px #00e67620;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .alert-banner {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .message-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .verdict-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>
